modules.description: Generates unique, URL-safe identifiers using the CUID algorithm, supporting customization of length and character set. Works with strings and byte sequences to produce collision-resistant identifiers. Used in distributed systems to ensure unique record keys and session identifiers.

Generates unique identifiers with methods to retrieve specific fields, create slugs, and produce full IDs. Operates on string-based data to ensure uniqueness and traceability. Used for creating consistent, human-readable identifiers in distributed systems.
